graph TD
    subgraph Client Applications
        A[Web/Mobile/SPA Client] -->|1. Redirect to /authorize| B(Authorization Server)
    end

    subgraph Authorization Server
        B --> C{Authentication & Consent}
        C -->|2. Authorization Code| D[Authorization Service]
        D -->|3. Token Request to /token| E(Database)
        D -->|4. Access Token, Refresh Token, ID Token| A
    end

    subgraph Resource Server
        F[Resource Server (User's Platform)]
    end

    A -->|5. Access Resource with Access Token| F
    F -->|6. Validate Access Token (Introspection/JWT Verify)| D
    A -->|7. Refresh Token Request to /token| D

    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style B fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style C fill:#ccf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style D fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style E fill:#fcf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style F fill:#9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px


